{"tid":471714,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"90%人坐公共交通  但私家車的士竟佔70%車流","createTime":"2017-11-17T13:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T16:53:56.000Z","uid":77905,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34e36e8ef7a73062a86a18af498c331aad953bbd","tid":471714,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/panels/tp/papers/tp20171117cb4-182-7-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Fpapers%2Ftp20171117cb4-182-7-c.pdf&d=s8cASOkyFee%2Bs%2BIn7cxY2v755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6c8cbcd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/panels/tp/papers/tp20171117cb4-182-7-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n政府的交通運輸政策，是以公共交通為本、以鐵路為其骨幹。現時每天有 1 200 萬出行人次（或逾九成出行人次）使用公共交通。相對公共交通工具，私家車、電單車和的士都是較私人化的交通工具，<span style=\"color: red;\">卻佔所有隧道的總交通流量約 73%</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mrkiad7s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmrkiad7s&h=58a7497c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/4/1492758712_0E-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F4%2F1492758712_0E-1280w.jpg&h=a014d121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e7fe8d7c5cf2e030546338998db17faec1060ff","tid":471714,"uid":42791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"一架巴士坐百幾二百人<br />\n一架地鐵坐千幾二千人<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad71d66c0249935d03e3c9775042208273416e17","tid":471714,"uid":